(43, 13, 31, 49, 3, 10, 10, 'glorified', 'Glory and Wisdom Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of glory and the revelation of God''s wisdom. In John 13:31, the glorification of the Son is emphasized, while Ephesians 3:10 speaks of making known God''s wisdom, suggesting a link between divine glory and understanding.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
