(43, 13, 32, 43, 12, 23, 23, 'glorified', 'Connection of Glorification in John', 'Both passages emphasize the glorification of the Son of man. John 12:23 introduces the concept of glorification, while John 13:32 elaborates on how God will glorify him.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
