(43, 13, 36, 61, 1, 14, 14, 'thou shalt follow me afterwards', 'Peter''s Journey of Following Christ', 'This connection highlights Peter''s understanding of following Jesus, as he acknowledges in 2 Peter that he must ''put off this my tabernacle'' as Jesus indicated he would eventually follow Him. Both passages emphasize the theme of Peter''s future journey in relation to Christ''s departure.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
